GVSU can be understood as a primary receiver of federal education funding. But the opportunity map does not stop there.

Programs buy things.

That means a program may need:

- Mentors
- Trainers
- Speakers
- Transportation
- Food
- Event support
- Technology providers
- Curriculum support
- Marketing support
- Local business partners

